track.name: Nice To Know You
comments: More like Nice To Know This Song Exists...haven't listened in awhile, glad it came on the radio earlier today, reunited!! Coincidentally, the "waking limb"/"pins and needles" part gives me chills that do in fact feel suspiciously like pins and needles...EVERY. TIME.
I'm not a large fan of Incubus, but this track rocks!!
"To obtain a bird's eye is to turn a blizzard to a breeze"...Oh man! *love*
I wish Boyd's attitude that comes across in his singing didn't put me off so much. The song's awesome but he sounds so....cocky. Always felt that about Incubus.
still in love with every song from morning view
great song, especially the intro. also, awesome drums throughout the song [2] One of my favorite parts next to... : Better then watching newborn Nebula's in bloom...
Am I the only one who finds it strange to open an album with a "goodbye"-song? :D
I remember hearing this song for the first time on a Miller Lite commercial back in the day.
great song, especially the intro. also, awesome drums throughout the song
I like his voice... [2] is breathtaking...
loves me a drop of Incubus............
